The management of the National Youth Service Corps, NYSC, on Monday, announced the date for online registration of prospective 2019 batch C corps members. The scheme also announced the closing date for online registration of prospective 2019 corps members The registration exercise will commence on Monday, October 21 till November 1, 2019. This was confirmed in a statement on Monday on the NYSC official Twitter account. Prospective corps members have been advised to register on the website www.Nysc.org.ng The statement read: “PUBLIC NOTICE: This is to inform 2019 Batch ‘C’ Prospective Corps Members that Online Registration commences Monday, 21st October to Friday 1st November 2019. “Visit registration portal www.Nysc.org.ng” Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.